title: Excludes from definition of "employee" such services rendered by various independent contractors who service the harness racing industry
summary: Excludes from the definition of employee such services rendered by a harness race driver, only a groom or caretaker of a temporary designated trainer of a harness race horse, a shipper or transporter of a harness race horse, a farrier of a harness race horse, or a veterinarian to a harness race horse.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the workers' compensation law, in relation to the definition of employee
